Not been able to run the code leads to a number of assumptions.

Based on you description, I would say you are blocking the Event Dispatching Thread while loading the image, this is going to prevent the UI from been updated.

See [Concurrency in Swing](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/concurrency/index.html) for more details.  I&#39;d recommend using a `SwingWorker` to actually load the image.

You should also be making use of [layout managers](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/layout/index.html), you&#39;d find [`CardLayout`](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/layout/card.html) especially helpful for switching between components.

